#: ../../../reference/swig.interface-file.rst:240
msgid ""
"Input arrays are defined as arrays of data that are passed into a routine "
"but are not altered in-place or returned to the user.  The Python input "
"array is therefore allowed to be almost any Python sequence (such as a list) "
"that can be converted to the requested type of array.  The input array "
"signatures are"
msgstr ""

