msgid ""
"In-place arrays are defined as arrays that are modified in-place.  The input "
"values may or may not be used, but the values at the time the function "
"returns are significant.  The provided Python argument must therefore be a "
"NumPy array of the required type.  The in-place signatures are"
msgstr ""

