"dimensions. One example is a \"quantization\" function that quantizes each "
"element of an array in-place, be it 1D, 2D or whatever. This form checks for "
"continuity but allows either C or Fortran ordering."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/swig.interface-file.rst:329
